    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="效果如图"><a href="#效果如图" class="headerlink" title="效果如图"></a>效果如图</h2><img src="https://photo-1253565044.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/CSS_2D%E5%8F%98%E5%BD%A2.PNG" class="[img]"><h2 id="2D-转换"><a href="#2D-转换" class="headerlink" title="2D 转换"></a>2D 转换</h2><p>2D 变换的方法有：</p><ul><li>translate()<br>  //translate(x,y)方法，根据左(X轴)和顶部(Y轴)位置给定的参数，从当前元素位置移动，单位：px。</li><li>rotate()<br>  //rotate()方法，在一个给定度数顺时针旋转的元素。负值是允许的，这样是元素逆时针旋转, 单位：deg。</li><li>scale()<br>  //scale(x,y)方法，该元素增加或减少的大小，取决于宽度（X轴）和高度（Y轴）的参数。</li><li>skew(x,y)<br>  //包含两个参数值，分别表示X轴和Y轴倾斜的角度，如果第二个参数为空，则默认为0，参数为负表示向相反方向倾斜,单位：deg。</li><li>matrix()<br>  // matrix( a, b, c, d, e, f );a 水平缩放,b 水平倾斜,c 垂直倾斜,d 垂直缩放,e 水平移动,f 垂直移动。</li></ul><h2 id="样例"><a href="#样例" class="headerlink" title="样例"></a>样例</h2><h3 id="HTML"><a href="#HTML" class="headerlink" title="HTML:"></a>HTML:</h3><pre><code>&lt;div class=&quot;div0&quot;&gt;  box0&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;div1&quot;&gt;  box1&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;div2&quot;&gt;  box2&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;div3&quot;&gt;  box3&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;div4&quot;&gt;  box4&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;div5&quot;&gt;  box5&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre><h3 id="CSS"><a href="#CSS" class="headerlink" title="CSS:"></a>CSS:</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">div&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  width: 100px;</span><br><span class="line">  background:#d0e0e3;</span><br><span class="line">  padding: 40px 0 40px 0;</span><br><span class="line">  text-align: center;</span><br><span class="line">  float: left;</span><br><span class="line">  margin: 200px 50px 0 0;</span><br><span class="line">  font-size:20px;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">.div1&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  transform: skew(30deg,0deg);</span><br><span class="line">  -webkit-transform: skew(30deg,0deg);</span><br><span class="line">  -ms-transform: skew(30deg,0deg);</span><br><span class="line">  -o-transform: skew(30deg,0deg);</span><br><span class="line">  -moz-transform: skew(30deg,0deg);</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">.div2&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  transform: scale(0.5,1);</span><br><span class="line">  -webkit-transform: scale(0.5,1);</span><br><span class="line">  -ms-transform: scale(0.5,1);</span><br><span class="line">  -o-transform: scale(0.5,1);</span><br><span class="line">  -moz-transform: scale(0.5,1);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">.div3&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  transform: rotate(45deg);</span><br><span class="line">  -webkit-transfoem: rotate(45deg);</span><br><span class="line">  -ms-transform: rotate(45deg);</span><br><span class="line">  -moz-transform: rotate(45deg);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">.div4&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  transform: translate(10px,20px);</span><br><span class="line">  -webkit-transform: translate(10px,20px);</span><br><span class="line">  -o-transform: translate(10px,20px);</span><br><span class="line">  -ms-transform: translate(10px,20px);</span><br><span class="line">  -moz-transform: translate(10px,20px);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">.div5&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  transform: matrix(1.2,1,0,0.8,20,60);</span><br><span class="line">  -webkit-transform: matrix(1.2,1,0,0.8,20,60);</span><br><span class="line">  -o-transform: matrix(1.2,1,0,0.8,20,60);</span><br><span class="line">  -ms-transform: matrix(1.2,1,0,0.8,20,60);</span><br><span class="line">  -moz-transform: matrix(1.2,1,0,0.8,20,60);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="实践"><a href="#实践" class="headerlink" title="实践"></a>实践</h2><p>点击这里<a href="https://codepen.io/chenguocaiyx/pen/bMOvvQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener">去实验</a>，创建一个Fork就可以进行修改了。</p>]]></content>
    
